p: Compared with free EA treatment, EFEN-treated cells had higher protein expression of cyclin B and cell division cycle-regulated protein 2 ( Figure 5(e)). EFEN might cause mitosis or division lag via activation of cyclin B/CDC 2. Compared with free EA, EFEN-treatment resulted in higher protein expression of caspase-3, -8, and -9, and lower protein levels of Bcl-2/Bax ( Figure 5(f)).
